## âš™ï¸ Deployment

### 1. Environment setup

sudo nano .env
pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m app.bot.init
2. Database migrations
Generate a new migration:


alembic revision --autogenerate -m "name"
Apply migrations:


alembic upgrade head
